**Do NOT use** when:
- Item 1

# After
**Do NOT use** when:

- Item 1
```

**MD034 - Bare URLs** (9 locations):

```markdown
# Before
- Docker Docs: https://docs.docker.com/build/multi-stage/

# After
- Docker Docs: <https://docs.docker.com/build/multi-stage/>
```

### Files Modified

```bash
