### Working Ruff Hook Configuration

```yaml
# .pre-commit-config.yaml
- repo: local
  hooks:
    - id: ruff-format-python
      name: Ruff Format Python
      entry: pixi run ruff format
      language: system
      types: [python]
      pass_filenames: true

    - id: ruff-check-python
